Package jcolibri.tools.gui.connector

Class Summary
FrConnector Frame to manage connectors.
PnlConnectorOther Panel to manage connectors of type "Other".
PnlConnectorSQL Panel to manage the SQL connector.
PnlConnectorText Panel to manage the plain text connector.
PnlConnectorType The panels to manage a type of connector must extends this class.
PnlOtherParams Panel to manage the parameters of a connector of type "Other".
PnlSQLDBTable Panel to manage the database table.
PnlSQLMappings Panel to manage the mappings of a SQL connector.
PnlTextMappings Panel to manage the mappings of a plain text connector.
TbSQLDBTable Visual table that displays the structure of a database table.
TbSQLMappings Visual table to manage the mappings of a SQL connector.
TbTextMappings Visual table of mappings for the plain text connector.
